Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与彩云国初代国王共同建立国家的八位仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称作 彩八仙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在国王死后便从皇宫失去了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留给后世的只有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王为了供奉他们而修建的仙洞宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据史书记载
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当出现被人称颂的君主的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩八仙就会在仙洞宫现身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬日已至 春日非晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶州州尹 郑悠舜求见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这十年来一直支撑着茶州
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是茶州府所有官吏衷心的感激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您成为了优秀的王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在登基典礼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还很生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起 终于有了现在这样的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很努力呢 圣上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为您会更生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后都要有这样的魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要做好觉悟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就都表示私下赞同了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故弄玄虚也无妨 请您御批
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是高兴的话 随时都可以回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会任命你为尚书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命我为尚书？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是很高的升迁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吏部工部两位尚书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯听他们两位直言的人真的太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这其中还是有点窍门的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后偷偷地告诉给朕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我做不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么父王十年来都对茶州保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王在等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着茶州的平定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到培养出下任丞相的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 为了下任登上王位的皇子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此一定要活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先王陛下曾对我这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来朕的继位 父王早就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对燕青的处置以及茶州新州牧的任命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是您做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于圣上的继位 再次表示由衷的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶州稳定之后 我和您约好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会为了您而回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于心地仁慈坚定的吾王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底表示忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果红蓝两家造反的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我会成为您的支柱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您已经回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚回来 秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖琅叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖琅这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得一见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去吗 秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是那么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 茶的话我来泡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在马上…就去准备茶水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邵可大哥的情况我了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着急的话就快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的木简 真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我说 我很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑 好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们红州的名产蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来红州的宅邸的时候 这是你最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此说来 玖琅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你总喂秀丽吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 难不成黎深和玖琅杠上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那个原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出门的话就带上几个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎兄长来过的事我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖琅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么急于下结论一点都不像你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提亲的事我和黎深都好好看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个样子就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姑且先不要管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽还不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她马上就要回茶州去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在告诉她也无济于事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也可以断言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在给秀丽看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会断然拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说她讨厌政治联姻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是那之前的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 现在的秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没考虑婚姻的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和黎深都过目了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后作决定的还是秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且可能会非常困难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎无论如何都要自己来承担呢 玖琅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍微信任一下哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那么着急 红家也不会有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邵可兄长也这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会长命百岁地做宗主的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的觉悟我是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时肯定有很多曾孙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下任宗主怎样都可以随便选出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邵可兄长成为宗主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的事我玖琅来做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽的事情我确实有些急切了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的想法不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽和绛攸的婚事对红家再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道绛攸并不笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已经说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然擅自说亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫擅自
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和夫人的婚姻不也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绛攸是认真的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依玖琅的性格虽然不会强迫别人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但会在无形中会给人压力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果绛攸和秀丽结婚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎深就和成了秀丽的公公呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽的话 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了秀丽 还有谁可以制得住黎兄长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 两人都跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你们两个要去全商联做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为春姬和英姬奶奶买点礼物什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那龙莲为什么跟来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高雅的清风呼唤我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有预感很快可以完成一首绝世的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 完成了绝对是大灾难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 龙莲 为了转换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我被树枝间悬挂的蜜柑的优美感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是这个蜜柑传达给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失败 本想让他冷静一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去推广一下新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 不过我要先去传达一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先在这里稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会让交涉成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上干部们让我把这个交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 知道悠舜不在才把我叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽 把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去皇宫见悠舜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…等等…秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珀明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么憔悴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是官吏的工作没做完而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你是在吏部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说绛攸大人最近很繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吏部尚书总是把工作交给他来做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来还是你的族人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是红家的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些凹陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…比起我更担心蜜柑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁不知道 我的出仕是红家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀明最初一心想着要出仕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.87,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去更高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到能去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是在国试中及第的我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 小动物还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个关于邪仙教的成员…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是根据彩八仙的传说来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过了漫长时间的仙人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地变成了邪恶的邪仙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有好好被供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就会降灾作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就要定期献上祭品之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙一点都不稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有急件到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石荣村的附近 秋末左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了雪狐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前说的原因不明的怪病有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让柴彰也看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让全商联在一两日内准备好药物和大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拟好送达那里的行程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有治疗的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请写信通知秀丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种病 是可以预防的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是人与人之间的传染
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患病的时间是秋末左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上数月的潜伏期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在冬天发病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 只要发病一次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知 是没有办法治愈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 早就到冬天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石荣村的人或许来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果是还没确认雪狐的村子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有治愈的方法是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知是这样的 但全国这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有大夫知道治愈的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性最大的地方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集全国最好的大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵阳的皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请秀丽为了拯救百姓向皇上请求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上派遣最好的医官来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 马上就写信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就以此事为最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳月 再一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是再一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠舜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽 来的正巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人让我给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的吗？谁给的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 不要说我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一个亲切温柔好听的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个怪人 不过并不是可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然情况不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么今天和蜜柑这么有缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠舜 吏部尚书是红一族的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 好像是个从来不工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在红家的叔叔正在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我父亲不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很能干很了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望可以转告那个人 让他好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做果然是太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使什么都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽温柔善良的的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会在短时间内传达到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吏部的官员们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会在近期内从繁重的工作中解脱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 比起吏部事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先把全商联的事交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和凛一起去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果只是把这个交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从柴凛那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在并不想和茶州州牧见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郑悠舜不来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被彻底地拒绝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在茶州建立学术机关的计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那种表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们的工作就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和全商联的交涉 我们不战而胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就可以回茶州了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郑悠舜大人 很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经到这个时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事情要做 今天就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…悠舜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是玖琅叔叔做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能合你的胃口就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我也想帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖琅说不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 龙莲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上刚才一起在街上走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去的地方是别处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙莲连招呼都没打就一个人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不一定合适又会吹着奇怪的笛子出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 今天在王宫里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃的蜜柑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信 工作居然做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为吏部尚书来说 这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绛攸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 绛攸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚书把贵阳卖的红州产蜜柑全部买了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在我和红秀丽说话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个无耻的家伙用蜜柑砸到我的头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀丽 我就是你亲切温柔完美的叔叔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 蜜柑是可以吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 悠舜暂住的官厅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全商联的那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说我们是全胜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好好地告诉我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰花的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:22:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八片花瓣和满月的光华
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.12,0:24:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是毫无保留的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.99,0:24:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.97,0:24:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为他是这世上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.29,0:24:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么可怕的表情


